title: Widespread Panic - 2013.12.31 - Philips Arena, Atlanta, GA
description:
Widespread Panic | 2013.12.31 | Philips Arena, Atlanta, GA

Set 1:	Journey Through The Past^, Don't Be Denied, Time Fades Away^, And It Stoned Me, Expiration Day, Pickin' Up The Pieces*, Blue Indian, Climb To Safety (46 mins)

Set 2:	Holden Oversoul, Who Do You Belong To?, You Got Yours, Papa's Home, Old Neighborhood**, Angels On High**, Devil In Disguise**, Tail Dragger** (52 mins)

Set 3:	Burning Down The House**^, Come On**^, Bust It Big**, Jack > Chilly Water > Surprise Valley, Pilgrims, Surprise Valley***, You Should Be Glad**, Love Tractor (90 mins)

Encore:	Stop Breakin' Down Blues, Ain't Life Grand

Notes:	* w/ Randall Bramblett on sax
** w/ the Megablasters on horns 
*** w/ the Megablasters on horns & Paul D'augustino on keys
^ First time played

Comments: Recorded from Sirius replay 2014.01.01 and does not include "Spill The                 Wine." (Possibly because of copyright issues) Also does not include New Year countdown.

    **Multiple clicks and dropouts in last set, but remains very listenable.**

Source: Sirius broadcast(mix of official soundboard and audience mike between songs that causes some echo)}Creative SB X-Fi Recorder}Audacity Editor
